query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android-asynctask',
'asp.net-mvc-4',
'css3',
'entity-framework-4',
'inner-join',
'jquery',
'sublimetext3')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Beta',
'Deputy',
'Fanatic',
'Great Question',
'Not a Robot',
'Unsung Hero')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
